<%-
  # Render the live per-user cluster status (same engine as the shell MOTD).
  # Runs as the user inside the PUN; vulcan-status caches + timeout-bounds itself.
  status =
    begin
      `timeout 8 vulcan-status --plain 2>/dev/null`.to_s.chomp
    rescue StandardError
      ""
    end
-%>
<% if status.empty? %>
## Welcome to Vulcan

You are signed in. Pick an app from the panel to launch an interactive session,
or use **Files** / **Shell** / **Active Jobs** above.
<% else %>
```text
<%= status %>
```
<% end %>
